QVD-Auth-Basic

A basic authentication plugin for QVD that authenticates users against the
QVD's internal user table.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc QVD::Auth::Basic

You can also look for information at:

      QVD home page
          %MORFEOURL%
      
      QVD blog
          http://qvdblog.qindel.com

